<![CDATA[ <img src="https://i2.milimaj.com/i/milliyet/75/460x340/633ffaec86b24a1404005de0.jpg"/><p>Edinilen bilgiye göre, vatandaşların ihbarı üzerine polis, Şahinbey ilçesi Yeşilevler Mahallesi 16 Nolu Cadde'de bulunan eve geldi. Evde 2 aylık erkek bebek bıçaklanmış halde ölü bulundu.</p> <p>Bebeğin baygın ve bitkin halde bulunan ve psikolojik sorunları olduğu ileri sürülen annesi hastaneye kaldırılırken, polis olay yerinde inceleme yapıyor.</p> <section class="insert insert-contents mceNonEditable" data-contents="%5B%7B%22_Id%22%3A%22633fd3e986b247423458b1d9%22%2C%22Title%22%3A%22Uykuya%20dalan%202%20ayl%u0131k%20bebek%20bir%20daha%20uyanamad%u0131%22%2C%22Description%22%3A%22Bursa%27da%20annesinin%20emzirip%20be%u015Fi%u011Fine%20yat%u0131rd%u0131%u011F%u0131%202%20ayl%u0131k%20bebek%2C%20g%F6t%FCr%FCld%FC%u011F%FC%20hastanede%20hayat%u0131n%u0131%20kaybetti.%22%2C%22Url%22%3A%22/gundem/uykuya-dalan-2-aylik-bebek-bir-daha-uyanamadi-6837152%22%2C%22ContentType%22%3A%22Article%22%7D%5D" data-files="%5B%7B%22FileName%22%3A%22555.jpg%22%2C%22ContentType%22%3A%22image/jpeg%22%2C%22ModifiedDate%22%3A%222022-10-07T07%3A25%3A06.646Z%22%2C%22CreatedBy%22%3A%22aer%22%2C%22Length%22%3A146341%2C%22ChunkSize%22%3A261120%2C%22MD5%22%3A%229b999d913fd2f35ddef3caf0c566fe41%22%2C%22Metadata%22%3A%7B%22Title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22Description%22%3A%22%22%2C%22EmbedCode%22%3A%22%22%2C%22Tags%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22Sources%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22Credit%22%3A%22%22%2C%22FileShowRelatedNews%22%3Afalse%2C%22Grade%22%3A%22%22%2C%22SponsorLogo%22%3A%22%22%2C%22SponsorText%22%3A%22%22%2C%22BtnText%22%3A%22%22%2C%22BtnRedirectUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%22_Id%22%3A%22633fd45286b247423458b1db%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22633fd45286b247423458b1db%22%2C%22Application%22%3A%22com.milliyet%22%7D%5D" data-properties="%7B%22Type%22%3A%22RecommendedNewsHorizontalCard%22%2C%22Theme%22%3A%22red%22%2C%22BoxTitle%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ButtonText%22%3A%22Haberi%20G%F6r%FCnt%FCle%22%2C%22SelectTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%7D" data-type="Content">